text: Lashana Rasheda Lynch Sole Lashana Lynch born in London in 1987. (born 27 November 1987) is a British actress. She played Rosaline Capulet in the ABC period drama series Still Star-Crossed (2017) and Nomi in the 2021 movie No Time to Die. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:British movie actors Category:British television actors Category:British stage actors Category:British voice actors Category:Actors from London
